Fiedler, Leslie. <I>The Stranger in Shakespeare</I>. New York: Macmillan, 1960.<P>

Heilein, Robert. <I>Stranger in a Strange Land</I>. New York: Berkley, 1961.<P>

Hughes, Langston. <I>The Big Sea</I>. New York: Knopf, 1940.<P>

______ <I>I Wonder as I Wander</I>. New York: Rinehart, 1956.<P>

______ <I>Not Without Laughter</I>. New York: Knopf, 1930.<P>

______ <I>Selected Poems</I>. New York: Vintage, 1974.<P>

______ <I>Something in Cowmon and Other Stories</I>. New York: Hill and Wang, 1963.<P>

______ <I>Tambourines to Glory</I>. New York: John Day, 1958.<P>

______ <I>The Ways of White Folks</I>. New York: Knopf, 1934.<P>

